==English==

===Noun===
'''cuticula'''
# (''on shoot, especialy leaves'') A layer of [[cuticular wax]]es and other long [[fatty acid]] chains --> water-repelling surface, protection from uncontrolled [[transpiration]], protection from mechanical and [[pathogen]] damage. Plants in extremely cold or extremely warm climates have a particularly thick cuticula.

